beautiful together.

19
00:03:31,208 --> 00:03:33,958
Now, please take your places.

20
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:38,250
The new girls too.
Stand in your voice groups.

21
00:03:38,833 --> 00:03:40,417
Okay, I'll help you.

22
00:03:40,708 --> 00:03:43,000
You can go here.

23
00:03:43,125 --> 00:03:47,042
And you, come here
