210
00:18:54,458 --> 00:18:57,167
Look, Lucia,
this is the Devil's Bridge.

211
00:18:57,625 --> 00:19:01,000
When they built it,
they had a pact with the devil,

212
00:19:01,125 --> 00:19:03,042
